---
title: One-Pan Trattoria Tortelloni Bake with a Crispy Parmesan Panko Topping
description: Think a cheesy stuffed pasta can’t get any better? What about baking it in a creamy sauce with a crispy topping? We’re obsessed! Here, we toss tender, cheese-stuffed tortelloni in an herby tomato cream sauce, then finish it with a layer of Parmesan and panko breadcrumbs. Once broiled, it turns golden and crunchy, making a showstopping topping that’s guaranteed to earn you plenty of oohs and aahs from your lucky fellow diners.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6203c47ca9edd825f02b3f54-66a31f0c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-trattoria-tortelloni-bake-6203c47ca9edd825f02b3f54-7b2458e9.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-trattoria-tortelloni-bake-6203c47ca9edd825f02b3f54
time required: 25 minutes
course: main course
cuisine: Italian
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 750 kcal
  fat: 41 g
  saturated fat: 23 g
  carbohydrates: 74 g
